title: Kinetic Red Orange Necklace
description:
Discover miniature modernist art for the neck! In a truly unique combination, translucent dyed resin is suspended on stainless steel, placing the focus of this feather-weight necklace on the beauty of balance and color. Handmade in Chicago.

Chain: 24 in. L

Pendant:  2.75 in. L x 0.75 in. W
